<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en"
    xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
    xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
    metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
    i18n:domain="launchpad">
    <body>
        <div metal:fill-slot="main">
            This is the Launchpad login service utilizing
            <a href="http://openid.net/">OpenID</a> technology.
            This site allows you to use
            <a href="https://launchpad.net/people/+me">your Launchpad account</a>
            to log into OpenID enabled sites around the internet including
            those run by Canonical and Ubuntu.
            <p>
            To learn more about using this service, please review the
            <a href="https://help.launchpad.net/OpenID">instructions</a>.</p>
            <p>
            Note that this site is meant to be called from an OpenID enabled
            service and therefore has no user facing functions.</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
